01/12/2004
TIRANA, Albania -- Local media reported Tuesday (30 November) that the prefecture of Thessaloniki has decided to compensate ethnic Albanians for damages they suffered during clashes with Greek football fans in September.
Prefect Panajotis Psomiadis invited all Albanians with damaged cars to file claims with the authorities.
(Albanian Daily News - 01/12/04;
Top Channel TV - 30/11/04)
